hrough civic and religious practices, to funerary ritual"--Provided by publisher.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aMaterial culturezGreecexHistoryyTo 1500. 0aCities and towns, AncientzGreece. 0aCemeterieszGreecexHistoryyTo 1500. 0aSocial archaeologyzGreece. 0aLandscape archaeologyzGreece. 0aGreecexAntiquities. 4aElectronic books.1 aNevett, Lisa C.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.8287082